    title: Biological and chemical weapons proliferation
    description: This dataset provides information on countries' activities on biological and chemical weapons. It draws on data from the Arms Control Association (ACA), the Nuclear Threat Initiative (NTI), the Center for Nonproliferation Studies (CNS), the United Nations (UN), and a few supplementary sources.
    citation_full: Our World in Data based on Arms Control Association (2022), Nuclear Threat Initiative (2022), Center for Nonproliferation Studies (2008), and the UN (2022).
